# txiki wurl: plain-C WHATWG URL parser replacing deps/ada (the ada-ectomy)
#
# Adds deps/wurl/ (~4.1k lines C11, zero C++) implementing the ada_c.h subset
# src/url.c consumes (58 functions), plus a TJS_USE_ADA CMake option
# (default ON = upstream ada; -DTJS_USE_ADA=OFF selects wurl). src/url.c
# compiles unchanged. Characterized against the frozen WPT golden
# (test/fixtures/url/golden-tjs-url.json, 1,317 cases): untagged 100%
# byte-exact incl. url.c's NUL/'??'/raw-byte quirks; the 112 nonAsciiHost-
# tagged cases give 79 exact + 34 loud accepted-rejects, zero value
# divergences (IDNA level L1' = RFC 3492 punycode + oracle-generated
# allow-bitmap; L2 full UTS-46 is the completion bar — seams marked).
# Effect: binary -542KB (-9.1%) and drops the libc++ dependency entirely;
# with -DTJS_USE_ADA=OFF the toolchain floor is a C compiler (no C++20).
# Grading driver: node deps/wurl/grade-golden.mjs <tjs>. Regen bitmap:
# build/tjs/tjs run deps/wurl/gen-idna-allow.mjs > deps/wurl/idna_allow.h
